Suggests:
 cortex-console,
 cortex-secops,
 cortex-llm,
 cortex-gpu-nvidia,
 cortex-gpu-amd
Description: Cortex Linux full installation - AI-powered server management
 This meta-package installs the complete Cortex Linux system with
 all recommended packages for server management, containers, monitoring,
 and GPU support.
 .
 Includes:
  - Everything in cortex-core (which includes Docker)
  - Container tools (buildah, skopeo)
  - Virtualization (QEMU, libvirt)
  - Network security (fail2ban, auditd)
  - Monitoring (Prometheus node exporter)
  - Web server (nginx) and TLS (certbot)
  - Database clients (PostgreSQL, MariaDB, Redis)
  - Build tools (gcc, g++, make, python3-dev)
 .
 For GPU support, also install:
  - cortex-gpu-nvidia (NVIDIA drivers and CUDA)
  - cortex-gpu-amd (AMD ROCm runtime)
 .
 For security operations, install cortex-secops.
 For AI/ML workloads, install cortex-llm.
